      = image_tag "authors-adam.jpg", class: "stretch round"
    .col-sm-7.col-sm-offset-1
      %b Adam Derewecki
      (Ron's youngest son and former student) earned his Bachelors in Computer
      Engineering from Case Western Reserve University.  Since graduating, he's
      worked at numerous software start-ups in San Francisco. His passion for
      improving the state of the education system drew him to this project.
